description: Pho-Jita Fusion is a truck on the streets of Houston serving Thai and Mexican fusion dishes. Their menu includes Pad Thai, Thai-style pho, and an assortment of fusion items, including Thaimales and torthais. They provide meals that pack a punch with flavor and spice! Their basil chicken with ginger rice and sunny side up egg proves that a nice light meal can still be incredibly tasty.
name: Pho-jita Fusion
